parameters:
\nw[Captain]There's a monster already, I'm counting on you
guys!
\nw[Captain]The next one is big, I'm counting on you!

\nw[Captain]Phew... I can't see it nearby anymore... If it
appears again, I'll report it right away, so take
a little break.
\nw[Captain]Damn it, let's return to the port for now!

\nw[Captain]Geez... Spare me the defeat. Make sure to defeat
the monster properly next time.
